General.Name: Rizzo Group AB (publ)
General.Description: Rizzo Group AB (publ) offers travel accessories, bags, and shoes and accessories. It operated through a network of 93 stores under the Accent, Morris, Rizzo, and NK Shoes & Accessories names in Sweden and Norway. The company was formerly known as Venue Retail Group AB and changed its name to Rizzo Group AB (publ) in December 2020. Rizzo Group AB (publ) is headquartered in Stockholm, Sweden.
